				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				The reason this weapon isn't magical is that you can do the quest at level 12 or so.  Questing for a magical weapon with 6/20 stats would at least be a level 20+ quest or require money.  Basically, if you think this should be magical, you probably also think that newbies who start the game should be given 3 pieces of their class only armor to start out with.  On top of that, let's add an 9/21 magical weapon to their bank accounts after they reached level 15 and if they camp a spot for 5 hours.<BR>
What I'm trying to say is you shouldn't expect too much from such a low level quest that doesn't require all that much effort.
